 "data": "@startuml Search System Sequence Diagram

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 100
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor \"User\" as user
participant \"API Endpoint\n/api/search\" as api
participant \"SearchService\" as service
participant \"ProviderRegistry\" as registry
participant \"EventBus\" as events
participant \"BackgroundTasks\" as bg

box \"Search Providers\" #LightBlue
participant \"ScientificPaperProvider\" as paper_provider
participant \"ClinicalStudyProvider\" as study_provider
participant \"DataDomainProvider\" as domain_provider
end box

box \"Schema Transformers\" #LightGreen
participant \"DefaultTransformer\" as default
participant \"CompactTransformer\" as compact
participant \"DetailedTransformer\" as detailed
end box

box \"Background Services\" #LightYellow
participant \"SearchHistoryService\" as history
participant \"SavedSearchService\" as saved
participant \"CollectionService\" as collection
participant \"SuggestionService\" as suggestion
end box

database \"Database\" as db

== Search Flow ==

user -> api: POST /api/search\n{query, collection_type, schema_type, filters}
activate api

api -> service: search(collection_type, terms, filters, schema_type)
activate service

service -> registry: get_provider(collection_type)
activate registry
registry --> service: provider instance
deactivate registry

alt collection_type == \"scientific_paper\"
 service -> paper_provider: search(terms, filters, page, per_page)
 activate paper_provider
 paper_provider -> db: execute query
 paper_provider --> service: raw_results
 deactivate paper_provider
else collection_type == \"clinical_study\" 
 service -> study_provider: search(terms, filters, page, per_page)
 activate study_provider
 study_provider -> db: execute query
 study_provider --> service: raw_results
 deactivate study_provider
else collection_type == \"data_domain\"
 service -> domain_provider: search(terms, filters, page, per_page)
 activate domain_provider
 domain_provider -> db: execute query
 domain_provider --> service: raw_results
 deactivate domain_provider
end

alt schema_type == \"default\"
 service -> default: transform(raw_results)
 activate default
 default --> service: formatted_results
 deactivate default
else schema_type == \"compact\"
 service -> compact: transform(raw_results)
 activate compact
 compact --> service: formatted_results
 deactivate compact
else schema_type == \"detailed\"
 service -> detailed: transform(raw_results)
 activate detailed
 detailed --> service: formatted_results
 deactivate detailed
end

service --> api: search results
deactivate service

api -> events: publish(\"search_performed\", {search_data})
activate events

events ->> history: handle(\"search_performed\", data)
note right: Asynchronous\nProcess

events ->> suggestion: update_suggestions(query, results)
deactivate events

api --> user: search results JSON
deactivate api

== Search History Logging (Background) ==

history -> db: log search history entry
activate history
db --> history: success
deactivate history

== Save Search Flow ==

user -> api: POST /api/saved-searches\n{query, name, filters}
activate api

api -> bg: add_task(process_save_search, ...)
activate bg
api --> user: {success: true}
deactivate api

bg -> saved: process_save_search(...)
activate saved
saved -> db: create/update saved search
db --> saved: success
deactivate saved
deactivate bg

== Collection Management ==

user -> api: POST /api/collections/{id}/items
activate api

api -> bg: add_task(add_item_to_collection, ...)
activate bg
api --> user: {success: true}
deactivate api

bg -> collection: add_item_to_collection(...)
activate collection
collection -> db: create collection item
collection -> events: publish(\"collection_updated\", {collection_data})
db --> collection: success
deactivate collection
deactivate bg

== Search Suggestions ==

user -> api: GET /api/suggest?q=term
activate api

api -> suggestion: get_suggestions(term)
activate suggestion
suggestion -> db: fetch matching terms and recent searches
db --> suggestion: suggestions
suggestion --> api: suggestions list
deactivate suggestion

api --> user: suggestions JSON
deactivate api

@enduml",
